{"tid":1511981,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"[夜晚10點;10點半嗌口號]小心提防...警察係警車入邊用望遠鏡監察嗌口號人士","createTime":"2019-08-27T16:51:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-27T17:39:36.000Z","uid":286589,"like":11,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"8b8fbab1f16b61b85d137857b0f9a3d889d2557b","tid":1511981,"uid":286589,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T16:51:51.000Z","msg":"代貼POST:<br />\n請大家小心提防，最近大家夜晚10點 10點半嗌口號已經吸引到警方的注意。<br />\n有朋友係長沙灣李鄭屋踢足球時見到，<br />\n時間10點30分有人係足球場大叫光復香港，<br />\n時代革命，樓上住戶都有回應，<br />\n叫左半分鐘後就走左，<br />\n隔左一兩分鐘就有警車過黎(圖中球場出入位置)，<br />\n朋友見到<span style=\"color: red;\">警察冇開門動作</span>，<br />\n只係<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">坐係車度用疑似望遠鏡監視足球場上的人</span></strong>，<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/agyg0Fr.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fagyg0Fr.jpg&h=dcee5007&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n停留左約5-8分鐘。<br />\n<br />\n停留其間有小插曲<br />\n <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SEnJFF6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSEnJFF6.jpg&h=267cd1cb&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n朋友對果隊龍門用腳掃跌朋友的隊友(圖中左邊圈A)，<br />\n有人大叫係咪要打交，<br />\n隔離就有警車係度，<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">雙方發生姿體衝突後，</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">跟住警車就走左...</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"107eb3d4dc7e0fe6487fb0dfa9b343299ea584e9","tid":1511981,"uid":55128,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T16:52:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PWzcvgg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPWzcvgg.jpg&h=187c67d0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n九月一號下午一點機場見<br />\n<br />\n901機場和你塞 Channel<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyou&d=hq0sVSmFYzKD%2BASQGeqgxvDXWQKahOldmH8%2Bpia8yKE%3D&h=c6dfeb02\" target=\"_blank\">http://t.me/stuckwithyou</a><br />\n901機場和你